       mesh programs such as [4mpicknps[24m.  Its purpose is to present the user with
       some  information  on  minimum  and  maximum values related to the mesh
       defined. These values may be of help for setting search criteria  in  a
       utility such as [4mpicknps[24m.  The values returned are:

       maximum element area
